      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033143,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b3a",
      "text": "  なんか回したくなった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b3b",
      "text": "  [ヒヤヒヤの遠心分離][Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b3c",
      "text": "  どういう成分に分離するのだろう笑[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b3d",
      "text": "  [ヒヒ]と[ヤヤ]に分離されるよ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b3e",
      "text": "  ほほう[ヒヒ.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b3f",
      "text": "  [ヒヤヒヤ.icon][$ \\xmapsto{\\text{遠心分離}}]([ヒヒ.icon], [ヤヤ.icon])[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b40",
      "text": "  code:mermaid",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b41",
      "text": "      %% h",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b42",
      "text": "      flowchart LR",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b43",
      "text": "         hy(\"<img src='https://i.gyazo.com/5e1e43dc3298a3d9378ebd578e78ca99.png' />\")",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b44",
      "text": "         h(\"<img src='https://i.gyazo.com/5d0af9e7409c418ae6e9bb85268e3a3e.jpg' />\")",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b45",
      "text": "         y(\"<img src='https://i.gyazo.com/2b80ceb83bf1ac4156e68be8fd76d4d2.png' />\")",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b46",
      "text": "         hy ---> X{遠心分離}",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b47",
      "text": "         X ---> |ヒヒ|h",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b48",
      "text": "         X ---> |ヤヤ|y",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b49",
      "text": "     ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b4a",
      "text": "\t\tヒエヒエな冷たい空気を送り込む[送風機]をイメージ。冬の空気を夏に送り込んでくれないかな[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b4b",
      "text": " [ヤヤ]さん、はじめまして[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14790000000000f44b4c",
      "text": "  とインデントしてリプライしようとしたらマーメイドだった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033145,
      "updated": 1772033145
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14770000000000f44b39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033143,
      "updated": 1772033143
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b27",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033119
    },
    {
      "id": "699f145f0000000000f44b37",
      "text": " もう1度[ヒヤヒヤの遠心分離]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033119,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b28",
      "text": " \t危惧、不安",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b29",
      "text": " \t\t関係が修復不能になるのではないか",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b2a",
      "text": " \t\t状況が制御できず、また undo もできないのではないか",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b2b",
      "text": " \t\tもしかしたら自分も巻き込まれるかも",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b2c",
      "text": " \t緊張、居た堪れなさ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b2d",
      "text": " \t\t当事者の立場に共感する（してしまう）",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b2e",
      "text": " \t防衛",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b2f",
      "text": " \t\t（たとえ自分に向けてでなくとも）攻撃だともし解釈した場合、身を守ろうとする",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b30",
      "text": " \t高揚",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b31",
      "text": " \t\t自分が当事者でなく傍観者ゆえ、[コロシアム]のようなドラマ性を見出してしまう",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b32",
      "text": " \t\t [井戸端コロシアム][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b33",
      "text": " \t\t  コロシアム端？",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b34",
      "text": " \t\t  [コロシアムと井戸の類似性]うける[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b35",
      "text": " \t——あれ？こういうこと書き出してるページ、他にもあったっけ。あった気がする。",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1772033097,
      "updated": 1772033122
    },
    {
      "id": "699f14480000000000f44b36",
